name: "MVC Portlet with DS and Freemarker"
description: |
  Demonstrates how to
    <ul> 
      <li> build a portlet with Liferay MVC framework </li>
      <li> use DS (Declarative Services) framework to register it </li>
      <li> use Freemarker templates for the view </li>
      <li> use language resource bundles </li>
    </ul>
displayFiles:
  - name: Documentation 
    highlighting: markdown 
    path: README.md
  - name: Portlet class
    highlighting: java 
    path: src/main/java/com/liferay/code/samples/portal/modules/applications/portlets/mvc_ds_freemarker/BlankFreemarkerPortlet.java
  - name: Freemarker init template
    highlighting: markup 
    path: src/main/resources/templates/init.ftl
  - name: Freemarker view template
    highlighting: markup 
    path: src/main/resources/templates/view.ftl
  - name: Bnd configuration
    highlighting: yaml 
    path: bnd.bnd
  - name: Maven POM
    highlighting: xml 
    path: pom.xml
  - name: Gradle build
    highlighting: groovy 
    path: build.gradle

